492	  /// @param  `dimensions` : A map specifying the number of levels,
493	  ///                      that is, the dimension of each degree of freedom
494	  ///                      that the operator acts on. Example for two, 2-level
495	  ///                      degrees of freedom: `{0 : 2, 1 : 2}`.
